      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "我们需要画一个工业物联网的数据流图，展示从边缘节点采集数据到最终控制执行的完整链路。起点是IoT_Industrial_EdgeNode，也就是边缘节点设备。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "A_T0_U"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 2,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "clarify",
      "utterance": "明白，边缘节点作为数据采集入口。那数据从边缘节点出来后，是通过什么形式传输的？我们需要标注这个数据流。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "A_T0_U",
        "A_T0_O"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 3,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "数据以TelemetryStream的形式传输，也就是遥测数据流。然后这些数据会发送到MQTT Broker进行消息中转。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "A_T0_O",
        "A_T0_C"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 4,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "好的，我已经把边缘节点、遥测数据流和MQTT Broker连起来了。接下来数据从Broker流向哪里？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "A_T0_U",
        "A_T0_O",
        "A_T0_C"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 5,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "MQTT Broker把数据推送给ActuatorController，也就是执行器控制器，这是控制指令的入口点。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "A_T0_C",
        "A_T1_U"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 6,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "ActuatorController已添加。我注意到后面还有一层控制逻辑，是PLC Logic吗？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "A_T1_U",
        "A_T1_O"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 7,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "对，ActuatorController把请求转换成PLC Logic，也就是可编程逻辑控制器的处理逻辑，完成具体的工业控制计算。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "A_T1_O"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 8,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "PLC Logic节点已加上。PLC处理完之后，控制信号回到ActuatorController执行物理动作，对吗？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "A_T1_O",
        "A_T1_C"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 9,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "没错，PLC Logic的输出回到ActuatorController，完成控制闭环。然后执行结果需要反馈回上游。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "A_T1_C"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 10,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "clarify",
      "utterance": "反馈路径是用TelemetryStream吗？还是从ActuatorController直接发？",
